    "Table 2, Ours model presented robust performance across several key indicators in the MOSEI dataset comparison.",
    "Notably, in accuracy and F1 Score, our model recorded impressive scores of 82.84%/84.81% and 83.01%/84.6%, respectively, indicating superior classification effectiveness.",
    "The model's MAE of 53.160 was competitive with the best performances, reflecting accurate prediction capabilities.",
    "It also achieved a high correlation coefficient of 75.980, demonstrating consistency in predictions.",
    "Facing the challenges of multi-category accuracy, our model continued to lead with scores of 55.500% and 53.880%, further underscoring its exceptional performance in emotion analysis tasks."
